    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>In geology, the discipline that studies and predicts the nature and operation of the forces by which the earth's surface are affected, as distinguished from the existing condition of the surface and the order and characteristics of the strata.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
